name: Hiragana World
description:
This is our Hiragana characters' home. Their planet's climate resembles ours on Earth. Something unique about this planet is that its clouds are still. Are they even clouds? Vegzi is still figuring it out. 
Note: Collectors from primary market get a special NFT #10 Vegzi's Hiragana Collection.
Medium: 1080x1080 MP4 without sound / Animated illustration loop / Artist: Vegzi / Twitter: @Vegzi1 / Created and minted: 25th of July 2021
